    • getAnimationLock

      @Nullable public @Nullable Duration getAnimationLock()
      Get the animation lock.

      Note that this is expected to be populated *after* this event is emitted, as this data is not known at the time of the original event. In addition, it may never be present, such as if you are importing a non-OP log, or an fflogs import.

      Returns:
      The animation lock, if one has been set.
      See Also:
